description:
Trump has created an opportunity for EU nations to attract the best and the brightest from the US. Our man in Europe gives that notion a thumbs up, while offering some advice for Americans who might be thinking the time might be right to get out of DOGE Dodge.

The post Europe Is Going for a Brain Drain Done Right! appeared first on FOSS Force.
title: Europe Is Going for a Brain Drain Done Right!

description:
It's all over until next year for Scale, the big, community oriented Linux festival for Southern California. Our man-on-the-scene filed the report before starting his long journey home.

The post SCALE’s Sunday OpenWrt One Keynote, Linux Training, and Another Trip to the Exhibit Floor appeared first on FOSS Force.
title: SCALE’s Sunday OpenWrt One Keynote, Linux Training, and Another Trip to the Exhibit Floor
